data.description: Perfect size one story 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom single family home in the Falcon Ridge neighborhood for a young family or retiree.  Nice covered front porch. This home features a spacious living room, a bright kitchen with ample cabinet space, island with bar and kitchen dining area. The primary bedroom offers a walk-in closet and an over sized walk in shower handicap accessible. The other two bedrooms share a full bathroom and have walk in closets. Large utility room has shelves for pantry and storage space. Heat and air conditioning system installed within the last 2 years. Conveniently located close to Lockheed, schools, parks, shopping, and dining. This is a History Maker home. floor plan same as redwood flipped. All offers will be reviewed.
